      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example boasts a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring pure mechanical engagement. The chassis is in flawless condition, having received proactive rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to exceed factory durability standards. Suspension geometry remains tight with zero bushing deflection, providing the surgical handling precision this platform is known for. A turn-key, high-revving masterpiece with original paint and meticulous service history.",
