      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior finish that retains its deep, showroom luster with absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Step inside to an interior that still carries the scent of new leather; the upholstery is supple with zero creasing, and every tactile surface\u2014from the steering wheel stitching to the console buttons\u2014feels crisp and unused. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. It drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line: the engine note is pure, the gear transitions are seamless, and the suspension remains perfectly taut. This vehicle has never seen a drop of rain, has never been smoked in, and has been pampered as a prized collector's piece. Included are all original manuals, a full set of keys, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a specimen that is virtually indistinguishable from new.",
